<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ظ ل ل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٢٨٢ - ظ ل ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ظلَّلَ يُظلِّل، تظليلاً، فهو مُظلِّل، والمفعول مُظلَّل <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ظلَّل الشَّجرُ:</span> أظلَّ؛ امتدّ ظلُّه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ظلَّله:</span> أظلَّه؛ غطَّاه بالظِّلِّ، ألقى عليه ظِلّه <span class="c1">"ظَلّلته الشّجرة- <span class="c3">{وَظَلَّلْنَا عَلَيْكُمُ الْغَمَامَ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• ظلَّل الرَّسمَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - جعل له ظلالا أو خطوطًا خفيفة <span class="c1">"ظلّل الصورةَ"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - عتَّمه <span class="c1">"أفكار مُظلَّلة: غير واضحة"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>